 THE WIRE - THE WIRE - THE WIRE - THE WIRE - THE WIRE - THE WIRE - THE WIRE
 
 
 Parallel Port                           Ti Link
   (Amiga)                                 (Ti)
 
 No Pin
                                                         _
                                                        / \ 
 3  -------------------------------------- Red ---------\_/
                                                        |#| 
 2  -------------------------------------- White--------| |
                                                        |_|
 21 -------------------------------------- Ground-\     |#|
                                                   \    | |
                                                    \   | |
                                                     -- | |
                                                        |_|
                                                      _/   \__________
                                                     /                \
                                                     |                ====
                                                     \________________/
                                                                                                              
                  As you can see : -no resistor
                                   -no diode
                                   -nothing
                                   
              why does the others use so much stuff when it's absolutely
       not necessary, I would never understand!
       
       PLEASE NOTE : this is an Amiga specific link, those lamers on pc
                     can NEVER use it ! (because of pc hardware !!! :-))))
      
       
       
   Since AmiTI V1.02 you CAN connect 2 leds BUT IT'S ONLY AN OPTION !
   They will flash according to what is recived or send !
   One flash when the TI is sending and one other when it is
   the Amiga.      
   
   AMITI **CAN** WORK WITHOUT THESE LEDs . 
       
   You should connect them like :
   
   		   
  20_____________|/|________
                 |\|        |
                            |
  19_____________|/|____    |
                 |\|    |   |
                        |   |
   5____________________|   |
                            |
                            |
   4________________________|
       
